## Typical Workflow

```bash
# 1. Initialize a new repository
purr init

# 2. Stage all files
purr add .

# 3. Stage specific files
purr add README.md main.go

# 4. View staged files
purr ls

# 5. View detailed file information
purr ls --debug
```

